MID_支援_ゼロ_ハロルド_Ｃ: $t1$Wmゼロ|7$Wmハロルド|3$w0|$Wsハロルド|$WaAh, Zero, my man.$k$pThis is the first time we've\nspoken alone, isn't it?$k\n$Wsゼロ|$Wa$E笑,|Right.$k$pWe may both be royal guards, but\nwe've never had any point of contact...$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E怒,|I've heard the rumors about you. What's\na wanted man doing in Leon's service?$k\n$Wsゼロ|$Wa$E怒,|Why does it matter?$k$pIt's not something that merits attention\nfrom a hero of the Nohrian peasantry,$k$pand I don't want to hear one\nof your spiels about justice.$k$pGuys like you are the type I hate most.$k$pYou can take your personal brand\nof justice and stuff it.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E苦,汗|It sounds to me like you're trying\nto agitate anyone who asks.$k$pIs that a habit among wanted men?$k\n$Wsゼロ|$Wa$Eキメ,|You think I'm agitating you?$k$p$Eにやり,|Is listening to me so pleasurable\nthat it gets you all agitated inside?$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E怒,|There, that's what I'm talking about.$k\n$Wsゼロ|$Wa$E笑,|This is enough to get you agitated?\nYou're cuter than you look.$k$p$Eにやり,|How about I ram something\neven better into you?$k$pRight into your cute little ears...$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E苦,汗|...They were right about you.\nYou really are unpleasant.$k\n$Wsゼロ|$Wa$E怒,|What?$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E怒,|You see, people have been\ncomplaining about the way you talk.$k$p$E通常2,汗|I came over to check it out.$k$pAnd here, I discover that you really\nare as depressing as they say.$k\n$Wsゼロ|$Wa$E通常,|So what of it?$k$p$E怒,|Your justice doesn't concern\nthe way people talk, does it?$k$pGet off my case.$k
MID_支援_ゼロ_ハロルド_Ｂ: $t1$Wmゼロ|7$Wmハロルド|3$w0|$Wsハロルド|$WaZero, my man, there's something\nI wanna ask you.$k\n$Wsゼロ|$WaUgh, what is it?$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E通常2,|Word is, there's a gang of thieves\nplanning a large-scale robbery tonight.$k$pThat band was declining for a while,\nbut lately they've grown in force.$k$pLet me give it to you straight―$k$pI'm thinking you're involved\nin their recent deeds.$k\n$Wsゼロ|$Wa$E怒,|Nope, I've got nothing\nto do with them.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E怒,|Should I trust you? This is the same\nband of thieves you were once a part of.$k\n$Wsゼロ|$Wa$E苦,|So what? Are you gonna doubt\nme thanks to my past?$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E苦,汗|I don't mean to, but...$k\n$Wsゼロ|$Wa$Eにやり,|If you don't trust me, then I could go\nbust into that mansion for real.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$Eキメ,|In that case, I'd have to deliver\njudgment unto you.$k$pI've received a request\nto stop these robbers.$k\n$Wsゼロ|$Wa$E怒,|...Hn.\nWhatever.$k$p$Eにやり,|Just try not to make it\ntoo easy for them.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E通常,|…………$k$p$E怒,|That's suspicious.$k\n$Wsゼロ|$Wa$E怒,|What is?$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E通常,|People who try to unnerve others like\nyou often have something to hide.$k$p$Eキメ,|They keep their distance from others\nso nobody can discover their secrets.$k\n$Wsゼロ|$Wa$E苦,汗|You think that nonsense passes\nfor actual theory?$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E笑,|Albeit, it's a theory I came\nup with on the spot.$k\n$Wsゼロ|$Wa$E笑,|Right, I thought so.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E怒,|I don't care what sort of life you lead...$k$p...but if there's something\nyou're hiding, speak now.$k\n$Wsゼロ|$Wa$E怒,|Persistent, aren't you?\nI'm outta here.$k\n$Wsゼロ|$Wd$w0|$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E苦,汗|Zero...$k
MID_支援_ゼロ_ハロルド_Ａ: $t1$Wmゼロ|7$Wmハロルド|3$w0|$Wsハロルド|$Wa...Zero.\nYou surprised me last night.$k\n$Wsゼロ|$WaHm?$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$Eキメ,|I experienced my usual bad luck, but even\nstill, I managed to corner the robbers.$k$pThen, right before I could\nend it all, you appeared.$k$p$E苦,汗|I thought, "I knew he was the one"...$k$pBut then you turned your back to\nme and started talking down to them...$k$p$E笑,|Truly an unexpected development.$k\n$Wsゼロ|$Wa$E笑,|I told you I wasn't\ninvolved with them.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E通常,|…………$k$p$E苦,汗|Not even in the lowest slums of Nohr is\nanyone unfamiliar with the infamous Zero.$k$pPerhaps I was too caught\nup in your past?$k\n$Wsゼロ|$Wa$E通常,|...I don't know what my parents looked like.$k$pMy father ran away before I was born.$k$pAnd by my very first memories,\nmy mom had vanished into thin air, too.$k$pThat gang of thieves was\nthe only home I ever had.$k$p$E怒,|But, one day... we snuck\ninto the Nohrian palace.$k$pWe grabbed what we were after,\nbut the guards found us.$k$p$E苦,汗|Then, my fellow thieves ditched me\nand used me as a decoy to escape.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E怒,汗|How ruthless...$k\n$Wsゼロ|$Wa$E通常,|And that was when Prince Leon\nappeared before me.$k$p$E怒,|His strength was beyond\nthat of normal men.$k$pI could tell at a glance how it would go\nif I fought him, so I told him to kill me.$k$pBeing abandoned by my own gang,\nI had nothing left anyway...$k$p$E苦,汗|But, my attitude seemed to catch\nhis interest, and from then on,$k$pPrince Leon posted me at his side.$k$p$E笑,|I died when my gang betrayed me...$k$pAnd then Leon saved me,\nand I was reborn.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E通常,|I never imagined you had such a past...$k$p$E笑,|Thank you for telling me.\nI see you had nothing to hide today.$k\n$Wsゼロ|$Wa$E怒,|What's that supposed to mean?$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$Eキメ,|You didn't use your usual, unpleasant\nmanner of speech one bit.$k$pThat's proof that you\nweren't hiding anything.$k\n$Wsゼロ|$Wa$E苦,汗|...The hell are you saying?$k$pIs that another one of your stupid\nspur-of-the-moment theories?$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E笑,|So what?$k$pJust because it's spur-of-the-moment\ndoesn't mean that it's wrong.$k$pI felt moved knowing that\neven you can speak properly.$k$p$Eキメ,|All right, now let's go tell everyone\nwhat we just discussed. If we do that,$k$peveryone will understand that even you\ncan talk properly in the right situation.$k\n$Wsゼロ|$Wa$E苦,汗|No way.$k$p$Eにやり,|Now get outta here unless you want me\nto plunge a thick arrow-shaft into you.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E笑,|...Woah there.\nI see you do have one thing you're hiding.$k$pBut that's cute, so I'll let it slide.$k\n$Wsゼロ|$Wa$E苦,汗|Huh? Cute?$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$Eキメ,|What you're trying to hide is\nyour own embarrassment.$k$pEmbarrassed from hearing my praise, you\nreverted to an unpleasant way of speaking.$k$pBut it's no use hiding from me.\nI can see right through you.$k\n$Wsゼロ|$Wa$E苦,照汗|Why, you...$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E笑,|Let's get along from now on.$k$pIf there's anything you need to talk\nabout, don't hesitate to ask me.$k$pAs a person who understands\nyour inner workings...$k$pI'll listen as long as\nyou need me to.$k\n$Wsゼロ|$WaTch...$k
